            FROM recent_thanked

            AND did_thank = $2
            AND at_time > $3
            AND server_id = $4

1a044b0aaffa9bc4d4db76cb23833aef50bbbe60.query:

        FROM thanked_users

228f28bc35aa52c4d5f557ff8b4ddf88e00b3d42.query:
INSERT INTO recent_thanked (user_id, did_thank, server_id, at_time)
                    VALUES ($1,$2,$3,$4)
                    ON CONFLICT ON CONSTRAINT recent_thanked_pk 
                    DO
                    UPDATE SET at_time = $3;

57d74a9dc469148550cfb303c4aca078131a33ba.query:
INSERT INTO thanked_users (user_id, times)
                VALUES($1,1) 
                ON CONFLICT (user_id) 
                DO 
                UPDATE SET times = thanked_users.times + 1;
